text.__SUMMARY__: Coccothrinax munizii is a species of palm tree that is endemic to eastern Cuba.  Like other members of the genus Coccothrinax, C. munizii is a fan palm.  It grows on rocky hills or in dry scrub forest on limestone.Henderson and colleagues (1995) considered C. munizii to be a synonym of Coccothrinax ekmanii.
